text: Juan Llabot was a sports shooter from Venezuela. Llabot competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. He was born on 29 June 1912 and died on 13 November 1995.Juan Llabot == References == Category:1912 births Category:1995 deaths Category:Venezuelan sport shooters Category:Olympians for Venezuela
